text: Dimitrij Nonin (born 5 April 1979) is a German gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Dnipro
